{
  "id": "10110",
  "key": "GG-107",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Create Logging System for Migration Activities and Issues",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use case:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Project Manager",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "I want to",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " have a logging system for migration activities and issues, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "so that",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " I can track the progress and troubleshoot any migration-related problems effectively."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance criteria:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "GIVEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " I want to log all activities and issues related to the Jira to Azure DevOps migration, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "WHEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the migration process is initiated, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AND",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " as each major activity is completed or an issue is encountered, "
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the logging system must capture the details and store them securely."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical notes:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The logging system should be implemented within the Node JS backend using a robust logging framework such as Winston or Bunyan. It should generate logs in a structured format and store them securely. Each log entry should include details such as timestamp, activity type, status, error messages (if any), and relevant metadata to aid in troubleshooting. Additionally, logs should not contain sensitive information such as credentials or API tokens to ensure security. The logging system should also support log rotation and archival to manage storage efficiently. Finally, the logs should be accessible to authorized personnel for monitoring and analysis purposes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
